Contract Addresses

Confirming your contract address when interacting with web3 wallets is an important step to ensure secure interactions with the DAO. By confirming the address, users can make sure that their transactions are going to the correct address and not being redirected to an address controlled by malicious actors. This helps to ensure that users' funds stay secure and that their transactions are going to the correct address.

Boostr
Eco-System

Boostr DAO is an eco-system that is designed to provide a hub for developers to build their own decentralized applications (DApps). The eco-system is comprised of 10% marketing, 20% staking, 40% eco-system, 20% p2e projects and 10% development team. This allows developers to create, launch and manage their own DApps, while providing them with the tools and resources they need to developand maintain the applications.


The staking system provides incentives for developers to remain active and engaged with the project, while the p2e projects allow developers to receive additional rewards for their projects. The development team is also involved in the project, providing technical and design support to ensure the success of the project. All of these components work together to create an efficient and effective eco-system.
